---
layout: layouts/_base.njk
title: Events
headerText: RxC EVENTS
introductionBlurb: |
  RadicalxChange hosts a monthly community meet up online, regular social events through our global communities, and conferences. We also co-present and participate in events in the civic tech ecosystem and support events organized by chapters and our community.

  We welcome everyone to join us: from artists, activists and academics to entrepreneurs, technologists, social scientists, and all those who don't fit in any neat category. If you can imagine a future in which we upgrade our social and institutional worlds, we're a home for you. Join discussions and actions which connect our growing plurality to our shared mission.

  Dig into our archives, tune in to our monthly community meet up [link to newsletter sign up], or join our next event.
---

<!-- prettier-ignore -->
{% import "components/introduction.njk" as introduction %}
